{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845834591,"sessionID":"ses_2875763a3ffexfWCih2BD8csre","part":{"id":"prt_d78a8fc82001P4QOnXuFMJBVQ5","messageID":"msg_d78a8f196001zq2qXXMlQvk5tA","sessionID":"ses_2875763a3ffexfWCih2BD8csre","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-81012f53df704675a93f7603934646b3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n2: \n3: **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n4: **Language:** Go  \n5: **Size:** S\n6: \n7: ## 共享类型定义\n8: \n9: ### 场景: 定义共享的 ConditionType 类型\n10: \n11: **GIVEN** pkg/apis 模块存在  \n12: **WHEN** 需要定义跨多个 CRD 共享的条件类型常量  \n13: **THEN** 创建 `types.go` 文件，定义 `ConditionType` 类型和常用条件类型常量\n14: \n15: ```go\n16: type ConditionType string\n17: \n18: const (\n19:     ConditionReady               ConditionType = \"Ready\"\n20:     ConditionProgressing         ConditionType = \"Progressing\"\n21:     ConditionDegraded            ConditionType = \"Degraded\"\n22:     ConditionAvailable           ConditionType = \"Available\"\n23:     ConditionInterpreterReady    ConditionType = \"InterpreterReady\"\n24:     ConditionRuntimeReady        ConditionType = \"RuntimeReady\"\n25: )\n26: ```\n27: \n28: ### 场景: 定义共享的 Condition 结构体\n29: \n30: **GIVEN** ConditionType 已定义  \n31: **WHEN** 需要定义跨多个 CRD 共享的 Condition 结构体  \n32: **THEN** 在 `types.go` 中定义标准化的 Condition 结构体\n33: \n34: ```go\n35: type Condition struct {\n36:     Type               ConditionType `json:\"type\"`\n37:     Status             ConditionStatus `json:\"status\"`\n38:     LastTransitionTime metav1.Time `json:\"lastTransitionTime\"`\n39:     Reason             string `json:\"reason,omitempty\"`\n40:     Message            string `json:\"message,omitempty\"`\n41: }\n42: \n43: type ConditionStatus string\n44: \n45: const (\n46:     ConditionTrue    ConditionStatus = \"True\"\n47:     ConditionFalse   ConditionStatus = \"False\"\n48:     ConditionUnknown ConditionStatus = \"Unknown\"\n49: )\n50: ```\n51: \n52: ## 共享常量定义\n53: \n54: ### 场景: 定义 API Group 和 Version 常量\n55: \n56: **GIVEN** pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 包存在  \n57: **WHEN** 需要在代码中引用 API Group 和 Version  \n58: **THEN** 创建 `const.go` 文件，定义 API Group 和 Version 常量\n59: \n60: ```go\n61: const (\n62:     GroupName = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n63:     Version   = \"v1alpha1\"\n64: )\n65: \n66: var (\n67:     SchemeGroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: GroupName, Version: Version}\n68: )\n69: ```\n70: \n71: ### 场景: 定义标签和注解键常量\n72: \n73: **GIVEN** 需要在多个 CRD 中使用标准化的标签和注解  \n74: **WHEN** 定义标签和注解键常量  \n75: **THEN** 在 `labels.go` 文件中定义标准化的标签和注解键\n76: \n77: ```go\n78: const (\n79:     LabelAgentName      = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/agent-name\"\n80:     LabelAgentType      = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/agent-type\"\n81:     LabelComponentName  = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/component\"\n82:     \n83:     AnnotationOwnedBy            = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/owned-by\"\n84:     AnnotationLastReconcileTime  = \"agentcube.volcano.sh/last-reconcile-time\"\n85: )\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ### 场景: 定义资源名称常量\n89: \n90: **GIVEN** 需要在代码中引用 CRD 资源名称  \n91: **WHEN** 定义资源名称常量  \n92: **THEN** 在 `const.go` 文件中定义资源名称常量\n93: \n94: ```go\n95: const (\n96:     ResourceAgentRuntimes      = \"agentruntimes\"\n97:     ResourceCodeInterpreters   = \"codeinterpreters\"\n98: )\n99: ```\n100: \n101: ## 共享辅助函数\n102: \n103: ### 场景: 提供条件状态更新辅助函数\n104: \n105: **GIVEN** Condition 结构体已定义  \n106: **WHEN** 需要便捷地更新条件状态  \n107: **THEN** 在 `conditions.go` 中提供条件状态管理辅助函数\n108: \n109: ```go\n110: func SetCondition(conditions *[]Condition, newCondition Condition)\n111: func GetCondition(conditions []Condition, conditionType ConditionType) *Condition\n112: func IsConditionTrue(conditions []Condition, conditionType ConditionType) bool\n113: func IsConditionFalse(conditions []Condition, conditionType ConditionType) bool\n114: ```\n115: \n116: ### 场景: 提供标签和注解辅助函数\n117: \n118: **GIVEN** 标签和注解键常量已定义  \n119: **WHEN** 需要便捷地构建和管理标签、注解  \n120: **THEN** 在 `labels.go` 中提供标签和注解辅助函数\n121: \n122: ```go\n123: func BuildAgentLabels(agentName, agentType string) map[string]string\n124: func AddOwnerAnnotation(labels map[string]string, ownerName string) map[string]string\n125: func HasAgentLabel(labels map[string]string) bool\n126: ```\n127: \n128: ## 最终验证\n129: \n130: ### 场景: 验证共享类型和常量的完整性\n131: \n132: **GIVEN** 所有共享类型和常量已定义  \n133: **WHEN** 运行 go build 和 go test  \n134: **THEN** pkg/apis 模块编译通过，所有测试用例通过，且无循环依赖\n135: \n136: ### 场景: 验证类型跨包可用性\n137: \n138: **GIVEN** 共享类型定义在 pkg/apis 中  \n139: **WHEN** 其他包（如 pkg/controllers, pkg/webhook）导入 pkg/apis  \n140: **THEN** 所有共享类型和常量可正确引用和使用\n141: \n142: ## 文件组织\n143: \n144: ### 场景: 文件结构清晰分离\n145: \n146: **GIVEN** pkg/apis 模块需要组织共享代码  \n147: **WHEN** 创建文件结构  \n148: **THEN** 按职责分离文件：\n149: ```\n150: pkg/apis/\n151: ├── const.go              # API Group、Version、资源名称常量\n152: ├── types.go              # 共享类型定义（Condition 等）\n153: ├── conditions.go         # 条件状态管理辅助函数\n154: └── labels.go             # 标签和注解键常量及辅助函数\n155: ```\n\n(End of file - total 155 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 — CRD 共享类型与常量\n\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S\n\n## 共享类型定义\n\n### 场景: 定义共享的 ConditionType 类型\n\n**GIVEN** pkg/apis 模块存在  \n**WHEN** 需要定义跨多个 CRD 共享的条件类型常量  \n**THEN** 创建 `types.go` 文件，定义 `ConditionType` 类型和常用条件类型常量\n\n```go\ntype ConditionType string\n\nconst (\n    ConditionReady               ConditionType = \"Ready\"\n    ConditionProgressing         ConditionType = \"Progressing\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775845834563,"end":1775845834589}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775845834594,"sessionID":"ses_2875763a3ffexfWCih2BD8csre","part":{"id":"prt_d78a8fe86001eJyyBvfSkHiY0C","messageID":"msg_d78a8f196001zq2qXXMlQvk5tA","sessionID":"ses_2875763a3ffexfWCih2BD8csre","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-365f7a760f6048288100c2219b5c4844","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md","time":{"start":1775845834567,"end":1775845834592}}}}
